<title>USA: Cable Design to buy back shares.</title>
<headline>Cable Design to buy back shares.</headline>
<dateline>PITTSBURGH 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Cable Design Technologies Corp said on Thursday that its board of directors has approved a program to repurchase up to $30 million of the company's common stock.</p>
<p>The shares will be purchased on the open market or in privately negotiated transactions, based on market conditions, the company said.</p>
<p>Cable Design Technologies currently has 18,349,708 shares of common stock outstanding.</p>
<p>Cable Design shares traded at 19-5/8, up 7/8, on 23,300 shares of volume.</p>
